      "title": "Neutrino Physics -Theory",
      "abstract": "We discuss recent developments in neutrino physics and focus, in particular, on neutrino oscillations and matter effects of three light active neutrinos. Moreover, we discuss the difference between Dirac and Majorana neutrinos, neutrinoless $\\beta\\beta$-decay, absolute neutrino masses and electromagnetic moments. Basic mechanisms and a few models for neutrino masses and mixing are also presented."
